%N A015267 Inverse of 1258th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015267 Periodic with period length 1258. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015267 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015267/b015267.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015267 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1258.
